--------------------------------------------------
GOAL
--------------------------------------------------

Develop a centralized Document Management System (DMS) that securely stores, organizes, versions, and manages files used across the entire application.

The module must support:

• Secure Upload
• Secure Download
• Versioning
• Categories
• Metadata
• Preview
• Approval Workflow
• Access Control
• Audit Logging
• Search
• Folder Management

